title: Pressure Point Therapy: The Complete Do-It-Yourself
description: pressure points are areas of stress held by the body. headaches, back pain, low energy, hormone problems and even sinus problems can result because of painful pressure points. in this book you will find out how you can use this therapy for yourself, family and friends. it is easy to learn and the color charts will show you which points to treat and in the correct order.
author: Michael Pinkus
